====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|musical instrument}} ''[[qin]]'' (“[[Chinese]] [[zither]]s”), referring to any of several [[traditional]] Chinese [[musical instrument]]s, most [[famously]] the ''[[guqin]]''
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[play]] the ''[[qin]]''
#* {{zh-x|^象 往 入 ^舜 宮，^舜 在 床 琴。|Xiang entered Shun's room, and found Shun on his bed '''playing the zither'''.|ref=Mengzi}}
# {{lb|zh|musical instrument}} [[collective]] [[name]] for [[certain]] [[musical instrument]]s, usually of [[string]] or [[keyboard]] types, such as [[piano]], [[organ]], [[violin]], [[cello]], ''[[huqin]]'', [[accordion]], [[harmonica]], etc.
#: {{zh-co|口琴|harmonica}}
#: {{zh-co|風琴|organ}}
#: {{zh-co|馬頭琴|horsehead '''fiddle'''}}
# {{lb|zh|musical instrument|specifically}} [[piano]] {{zh-mw|c:部}}
#: {{zh-co|三角琴|grand '''piano'''}}
#: {{zh-co|練 琴|to practise playing the '''piano'''|C}}
#: {{zh-x|我 學 過 兩 年 琴。|I learned to play the '''piano''' for two years.|C}}

